data.description: Beautifully maintained, this spacious end-unit townhouse has everything you need for comfortable one-level living! Fresh paint & luxury plank floors frame the elevated ceiling of the main living & dining area. The fully renovated kitchen features granite countertops, stainless appliances, a large peninsula for storage & seating, recessed lights & crown molding. The main level bedroom suite has brand new flooring & bathroom vanity, a large soaking tub, shower & walk-in closet. Upstairs you'll find a flexible loft space & two more bedrooms as well as a full bath w/ double sinks. The huge unfinished lower level is plumbed for a full bath & wet bar and would make an excellent gameroom. Large deck w/ lighting & a fabulous yard await your party guests. Georgetown Estates offers a great lifestyle including grass cutting, maintenance of shingles, siding & gutters, as well as pools, tennis, pickleball, & clubhouse rental!
